022import static java.util.Arrays.stream;
023import static java.util.stream.Collectors.toList;
024import static org.apiguardian.api.API.Status.INTERNAL;
025import static org.apiguardian.api.API.Status.STABLE;
026import static org.tquadrat.foundation.lang.Objects.checkState;
027import static org.tquadrat.foundation.lang.Objects.nonNull;
028import static org.tquadrat.foundation.lang.Objects.requireNonNullArgument;
029
030import java.io.UncheckedIOException;
031import java.lang.reflect.Modifier;
032import java.lang.reflect.ParameterizedType;
033import java.lang.reflect.Type;
034import java.util.ArrayList;
035import java.util.List;
036import java.util.Map;
037import java.util.Optional;
038
039import org.apiguardian.api.API;
040import org.tquadrat.foundation.annotation.ClassVersion;
041import org.tquadrat.foundation.exception.ValidationException;
042import org.tquadrat.foundation.javacomposer.AnnotationSpec;
043import org.tquadrat.foundation.javacomposer.ClassName;
044import org.tquadrat.foundation.javacomposer.ParameterizedTypeName;
045import org.tquadrat.foundation.javacomposer.TypeName;
046import org.tquadrat.foundation.javacomposer.TypeVariableName;

048/**
049 *  The implementation of
050 *  {@link TypeNameImpl}
051 *  for parameterised types.
052 *
053 *  @modified Thomas Thrien - thomas.thrien@tquadrat.org
054 *  @version $Id: ParameterizedTypeNameImpl.java 1085 2024-01-05 16:23:28Z tquadrat $
055 *  @since 0.0.5
056 *
057 *  @UMLGraph.link
058 */
059@ClassVersion( sourceVersion = "$Id: ParameterizedTypeNameImpl.java 1085 2024-01-05 16:23:28Z tquadrat $" )
060@API( status = INTERNAL, since = "0.0.5" )
061public final class ParameterizedTypeNameImpl extends TypeNameImpl implements ParameterizedTypeName
062{
063        /*------------*\
064    ====** Attributes **=======================================================
065        \*------------*/
066    /**
067     *  The enclosing type, if any.
068     */
069    @SuppressWarnings( "OptionalUsedAsFieldOrParameterType" )
070    private final Optional<ParameterizedTypeNameImpl> m_EnclosingType;
071
072    /**
073     *  The class name for this type.
074     */
075    @SuppressWarnings( "UseOfConcreteClass" )
076    private final ClassNameImpl m_RawType;
077
078    /**
079     *  The type arguments.
080     */
081    private final List<TypeNameImpl> m_TypeArguments;
082
083        /*--------------*\
084    ====** Constructors **=====================================================
085        \*--------------*/
086    /**
087     *  Creates a new {@code ParameterizedTypeNameImpl} instance.
088     *
089     *  @param  enclosingType   The optional enclosing type for this instance.
090     *  @param  rawType The class name for this instance.
091     *  @param  typeArguments   The type arguments.
092     */
093    @SuppressWarnings( "UseOfConcreteClass" )
094    public ParameterizedTypeNameImpl( final ParameterizedTypeNameImpl enclosingType, final ClassNameImpl rawType, final List<? extends TypeNameImpl> typeArguments )
095    {
096        this( enclosingType, rawType, typeArguments, new ArrayList<>() );
097    }   //  ParameterizedTypeNameImpl()
098
099    /**
100     *  Creates a new {@code ParameterizedTypeNameImpl} instance.
101     *
102     *  @param  enclosingType   The optional enclosing type for this instance.
103     *  @param  rawType The class name for this instance.
104     *  @param  typeArguments   The type arguments.
105     *  @param  ignored The annotations.
106     */
107    @SuppressWarnings( "UseOfConcreteClass" )
108    private ParameterizedTypeNameImpl( final ParameterizedTypeNameImpl enclosingType, final ClassNameImpl rawType, final List<? extends TypeNameImpl> typeArguments, final List<AnnotationSpecImpl> ignored )
109    {
110        this( Optional.ofNullable( enclosingType ), rawType, typeArguments, new ArrayList<>() );
111    }   //  ParameterizedTypeNameImpl()
112
113    /**
114     *  Creates a new {@code ParameterizedTypeNameImpl} instance.
115     *
116     *  @param  enclosingType   The optional enclosing type for this instance.
117     *  @param  rawType The class name for this instance.
118     *  @param  typeArguments   The type arguments.
119     *  @param  annotations The annotations.
120     */
121    @SuppressWarnings( {"OptionalUsedAsFieldOrParameterType", "UseOfConcreteClass"} )
122    private ParameterizedTypeNameImpl( final Optional<ParameterizedTypeNameImpl> enclosingType, final ClassNameImpl rawType, final List<? extends TypeNameImpl> typeArguments, final List<AnnotationSpecImpl> annotations )
123    {
124        super( annotations );
125        m_RawType = requireNonNullArgument( rawType, "rawType" ).annotated( annotations.stream().map( a -> (AnnotationSpec) a ).collect( toList() ) );
126        m_EnclosingType = enclosingType;
127        m_TypeArguments = List.copyOf( requireNonNullArgument( typeArguments, "typeArguments" ) );
128
129        checkState( !m_TypeArguments.isEmpty() || enclosingType.isPresent(), () -> new ValidationException( "no type arguments: %s".formatted( rawType ) ) );
130        for( final var typeArgument : m_TypeArguments )
131        {
132            checkState( !typeArgument.isPrimitive() && (typeArgument != VOID_PRIMITIVE), () -> new ValidationException( "invalid type parameter: %s".formatted( typeArgument ) ) );
133        }
134    }   //  ParameterizedTypeNameImpl()
135
136        /*---------*\
137    ====** Methods **==========================================================
138        \*---------*/
139    /**
140     *  {@inheritDoc}
141     */
142    @Override
143    public final ParameterizedTypeNameImpl annotated( final List<AnnotationSpec> annotations )
144    {
145        final var retValue = new ParameterizedTypeNameImpl( m_EnclosingType, m_RawType, m_TypeArguments, concatAnnotations( annotations ) );
146
147        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
148        return retValue;
149    }   //  annotated()
150
151    /**
152     *  {@inheritDoc}
153     */
154    @SuppressWarnings( {"PublicMethodNotExposedInInterface", "UseOfConcreteClass"} )
155    @Override
156    public final CodeWriter emit( final CodeWriter out ) throws UncheckedIOException
157    {
158        final var retValue = requireNonNullArgument( out, "out" );
159        if( m_EnclosingType.isPresent() )
160        {
161            m_EnclosingType.get().emit( retValue );
162            retValue.emit( "." );
163            if( isAnnotated() )
164            {
165                retValue.emit( " " );
166                emitAnnotations( retValue );
167            }
168            retValue.emit( m_RawType.simpleName() );
169        }
170        else
171        {
172            m_RawType.emit( retValue );
173        }
174
175        if( !m_TypeArguments.isEmpty() )
176        {
177            retValue.emitAndIndent( "<" );
178            var firstParameter = true;
179            for( final var parameter : m_TypeArguments )
180            {
181                if( !firstParameter ) retValue.emitAndIndent( ", " );
182                parameter.emit( retValue );
183                firstParameter = false;
184            }
185            retValue.emitAndIndent( ">" );
186        }
187
188        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
189        return retValue;
190    }   //  emit()
191
192    /**
193     *  Returns a parameterised type, applying the given type arguments to the
194     *  given raw type.
195     *
196     *  @param  rawType The class name for the new type.
197     *  @param  typeArguments   The type arguments.
198     *  @return The new instance of {@code ParameterizedTypeName}.
199     */
200    @API( status = STABLE, since = "0.2.0" )
201    public static final ParameterizedTypeNameImpl from( final Class<?> rawType, final Type... typeArguments )
202    {
203        final var retValue = new ParameterizedTypeNameImpl( null, (ClassNameImpl) ClassName.from( rawType ), list( typeArguments ) );
204
205        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
206        return retValue;
207    }   //  from()
208
209    /**
210     *  Returns a parameterised type, applying the given type arguments to the
211     *  given raw type.
212     *
213     *  @param  rawType The class name for the new type.
214     *  @param  typeArguments   The type arguments.
215     *  @return The new instance of {@code ParameterizedTypeName}.
216     */
217    @API( status = STABLE, since = "0.2.0" )
218    public static final ParameterizedTypeNameImpl from( final ClassName rawType, final TypeName... typeArguments )
219    {
220        final var retValue = new ParameterizedTypeNameImpl( null, (ClassNameImpl) rawType, stream( requireNonNullArgument( typeArguments, "typeArguments" ) ).map( t -> (TypeNameImpl) t ).collect( toList() ) );
221
222        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
223        return retValue;
224    }   //  from()
225
226    /**
227     *  Returns a parameterised type equivalent to the given type, with the
228     *  given type arguments added.
229     *
230     *  @param  type    The other type.
231     *  @param  typeArguments   The type arguments.
232     *  @return The new instance of {@code ParameterizedTypeName}.
233     */
234    @API( status = STABLE, since = "0.2.0" )
235    public static final ParameterizedTypeNameImpl from( final ParameterizedType type, final Map<Type,TypeVariableName> typeArguments )
236    {
237        final var rawType = (ClassNameImpl) ClassName.from( (Class<?>) type.getRawType() );
238        final var ownerType = (type.getOwnerType() instanceof ParameterizedType) && !Modifier.isStatic( ((Class<?>) type.getRawType()).getModifiers() ) ? (ParameterizedType) type.getOwnerType() : null;
239        final var typeArgumentList = TypeNameImpl.list( type.getActualTypeArguments(), typeArguments );
240        final var retValue = nonNull( ownerType )
241            ? from( ownerType, typeArguments ).nestedClass( rawType.simpleName(), typeArgumentList.stream().map( t -> (TypeName) t ).collect( toList() ) )
242            : new ParameterizedTypeNameImpl( null, rawType, typeArgumentList );
243
244        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
245        return retValue;
246    }   //  from()
247
248    /**
249     *  {@inheritDoc}
250     */
251    @Override
252    public final ParameterizedTypeNameImpl nestedClass( final CharSequence name )
253    {
254        final var retValue = new ParameterizedTypeNameImpl( this, m_RawType.nestedClass( requireNonNullArgument( name, "name" ) ), new ArrayList<>(), new ArrayList<>() );
255
256        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
257        return retValue;
258    }   //  nestedClass()
259
260    /**
261     *  {@inheritDoc}
262     */
263    @Override
264    public final ParameterizedTypeNameImpl nestedClass( final CharSequence name, final List<TypeName> typeArguments )
265    {
266        final var retValue = new ParameterizedTypeNameImpl( this, m_RawType.nestedClass( requireNonNullArgument( name, "name" ) ), typeArguments.stream().map( t -> (TypeNameImpl) t ).collect( toList() ), new ArrayList<>() );
267
268        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
269        return retValue;
270    }   //  nestedClass()
271
272    /**
273     *  {@inheritDoc}
274     */
275    @Override
276    public final ClassNameImpl rawType() { return m_RawType; }
277
278    /**
279     *  {@inheritDoc}
280     */
281    @Override
282    public final List<TypeName> typeArguments()
283    {
284        final var retValue = m_TypeArguments.stream()
285            .map( typeArgument -> (TypeName) typeArgument )
286            .toList();
287
288        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
289        return retValue;
290    }   //  typeArguments()
291
292    /**
293     *  {@inheritDoc}
294     */
295    @Override
296    public final ParameterizedTypeNameImpl withoutAnnotations()
297    {
298        final var retValue = new ParameterizedTypeNameImpl( m_EnclosingType, m_RawType.withoutAnnotations(), m_TypeArguments, new ArrayList<>() );
299
300        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
301        return retValue;
302    }   //  withoutAnnotations()
303}
304//  class ParameterizedTypeNameImpl
